    • registerEndpoint

      public void registerEndpoint(AzureListenerEndpoint endpoint, @Nullable MessageListenerContainerFactory<?> factory)
      Register a new AzureListenerEndpoint alongside the MessageListenerContainerFactory to use to create the underlying container.

      The factory may be null if the default factory has to be used for that endpoint.

      Parameters:
      endpoint - the AzureListenerEndpoint instance to register.
      factory - the MessageListenerContainerFactory to use.
